Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:35.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Rukia enter the Soul Society\Nin pursuit of Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They disrupt the marriage ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but are confronted by\NSoi Fon and Squad 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:43.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who were secretly assigned to\Nguard the premises, and a fight breaks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:47.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, they become fugitives\Non the run from the Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet up in\Na place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:02:01.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After being persuaded by Shu,\NAmagai agrees to side with Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nare thrown into confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,while trying to capture Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:13.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Kira, who is pursuing Kibune\Nfor his recent suspicious activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:18.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,happens to come across the place where\Nthe real Rurichiyo is being held,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and he battles the Kasumiohji’s assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:26.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon defeating the assassins,\NKira is confronted by Kibune,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who reveals his true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:44.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, everything you do\Nis always too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:50.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess left long ago,\NLieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that’s happened\Nis your doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Group One will cover from here\Nto Section Five East.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Group Two to Section Eight South,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Group Three go from\NSection Four West to Fifth Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Group Four go around to\NSection Three North.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Section Two North,\NCentral Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:31.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.\NThat’s under Squad 8’s jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:35.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it’s not that far from\NGroup Four’s assigned section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:36.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move in a section outside\Nof your jurisdiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll only get into trouble\Nwith the other squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:41.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:42.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The chaos within the Seireitei\Nhas been contained
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to the work of\Nthe Punishment Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Deployment of each squad to\Ntheir assigned sections has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now commencing a widespread manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:28.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our squad isn’t ready to deploy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?\NYou have a glum look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to talk with Genryusai Sensei again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he would not listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Yama is a stubborn one\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason that\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan is off limits to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I also did some investigating,\Nbut you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:56.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems they’re not\Nan easy clan to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re high-ranking aristocrats,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,yet they rarely present themselves\Nin front of the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:08.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And they aren’t associated with\NCentral 46 that much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:15.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I must say, Ichigo sure brings\Ntrouble with him every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get attacked from\Nthe outside at a time like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:25.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if that’s the issue\NSquad 12 is on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed Captain Kurotsuchi was\Nnot too eager to get involved
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the mess going on within\Nthe Seireitei anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we just need to do our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a Hell Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that while Kira\Nwas going after Kibune,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he found Rurichiyo Kasumiohji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:05.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On the premises of the Squad 3 barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As we suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s a high probability that Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is somehow involved with all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai, I’m sorry, but there’s no time\Nto get depressed about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s rescue Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this is misconduct\Ncaused by my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry! It’s that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn’t Squad 3 be located\Nstraight in this direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll end up passing through\Nthe section assigned to Squad 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have they all become\Nassigned to sections?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows that\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,won’t be disjointed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:51.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a little space in between\Neach assigned section.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we move through those areas,\Nwe won’t encounter anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:04.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kenny,\Naren’t you going after Itchy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also present during
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ama-Ama’s Captain’s Exam, right, Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ama-Ama is on the run with Itchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn’t they find\Nyou responsible, Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just tricked into it by the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You all received word from Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nlet’s head to the fighting arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They were carrying someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Ruricchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, look after Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I’ll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:12.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:15.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida, Inose, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, go to Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:21.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, take Sir Kannogi with you\Nand follow behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:21.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:24.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you fended off my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s just what\Nyou’d expect from a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them Bakkoutos,\Nalbeit a scaled-down version.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems it was too much\Nfor these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:57.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kasumiohji Clan. Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, but please die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Captain Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s going after the princess\Nwith Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The message made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is going on here, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:41.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:42.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune is our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what Lieutenant Kira says true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be in trouble depending\Non your response!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You small fish are shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll kill you all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampage, Reppu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head, Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dull-edged sword is\Nuseless before my Reppu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You… What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:59.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Wabisuke doubles\Nthe weight of the object it slashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash it a second time,\Nand it doubles again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash it a third time,\Nand it doubles yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer use that weapon now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it’s become super-heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:14.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune, you will now tell us\Nwhat your objective is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do by working\Nwith the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, what is the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:26.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the Kasumiohji Clan\Ndoes is none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they possess tremendous power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:34.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to use that power\Nand become even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To become the strongest Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:43.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:25.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What tremendous power.\NNot even Wabisuke works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Lieutenant Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me you’re dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kibune’s Zanpakuto is strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t die this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s useless to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it and you will have a swift death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:14.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your powers are\Nno match for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:24.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Izuru Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted\Nthe Kasumiohji’s power, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:37.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I saw,\Nyou already have enough power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have that much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn’t you use it for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Power, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to sacrifice to attain my Reppu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 31: Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reppu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“What,” you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Bakkouto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:24.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the great sword created
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the secret technique of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That vicious Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just like those assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:44.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That only substituted for the lack of\Nfighting skills for lowly individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who couldn’t even use a Shikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But this Bakkouto utilizes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my Spiritual Pressure and can grow endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your techniques will\Nnot work against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you possess such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:00.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Why,” you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To have power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:10.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. Power.\NIt’s about power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one recognized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was in\Nthe Soul Reaper Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always at the top of\Nmy class in academics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I never got a call from\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,during my academy years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can’t I join\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other high achievers in the past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all got in at the time of their graduation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are indeed a high achiever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that’s not the only qualification.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to think hard\Nabout what you lack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I supposed to be lacking?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In days of idleness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to train painstakingly for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After attaining a Shikai,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally accepted to a squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter what the situation was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed Hollows more than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My style of fighting was brought\Ninto question within the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:53.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of being promoted
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I faced the danger of being banished\Nfrom the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do you sacrifice\Nyour fellow squad members?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because they lack power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then isn’t it the responsibility\Nof those who have power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to save those who don’t?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I managed to avoid\Nbeing discharged,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was still sentenced to probation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never to become a Seat Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,While other less skilled members\Nmoved up in ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost my place within the squad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and received orders to join\Nthe Expedition Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In my despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed with the Expedition Unit\Nand continued killing Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To get back at those\Nwho didn’t recognize my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:51.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, I encountered this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:30.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With this power, no one will ever\Nbe able to ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:39.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I need even greater power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:52.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With that power, I will make\Nevery Soul Reaper recognize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That sword…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:58.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It has consumed his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like you who have no talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet get promoted to lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sweep all of you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you doesn’t deserve\Nto be where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When the previous captain went\Nout of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn’t even stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless people like you\Ndon’t deserve to stand above me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:40.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The killing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Yama sure is persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I received another reminder\Nto deploy my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:25.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to see\Nhow things play out a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:28.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’m starting to run out of excuses\Nto hold off the deployment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we try,\N“they just left a moment ago”?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t like talking over the phone,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy Encyclopedia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is about the costume\Nworn by a Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The costume design can vary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:45.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,depending on contemporary times\Nand individual tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:48.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it’s fundamental design\Nremains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:52.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We take pride in our costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:58.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I present to you\NRyuken Ishida in his costume gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:02.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you holding out for, huh?!